OL,3,CIsland loses its only dairy after
OL,4,Cnational appeal to find new farmers
OL,5,Cfails
OL,7,FThe search to replace Sark's outgoing
OL,8,Fdairy farmers has failed, meaning the
OL,9,Fisland will no longer produce its own
OL,10,Fmilk.
OL,12,FAt the end of April 2025, Jason and
OL,13,FKatherine Salisbury will return to
OL,14,Ftheir Suffolk farm.
OL,16,FThe couple have run Sark Dairy for the
OL,17,Flast 5 years, starting their tenure
OL,18,Fduring the pandemic.
