OL,3,CIsland loses its only dairy after
OL,4,Cnational appeal to find new farmers
OL,5,Cfails
OL,7,FSeveral of their animals will return
OL,8,Fto the mainland with them, but others
OL,9,Fwill be killed for beef.
OL,11,FJason says: "The dairy itself as a
OL,12,Fmilking unit will shut its doors, and
OL,13,Fthat'll be the end of any milking cows
OL,14,Ffor the time being.
OL,16,F"But there is a beef unit being born
OL,17,Fat the moment, and so we're keeping
OL,18,Four cold cows, and our dairy bull
OL,19,Fcalves will stay here - and that will
OL,20,Fbe local employment for the local lads
OL,21,Fthat will keep the abattoir going.
