OL,5,Cfails
OL,7,F"It will also be great for the
OL,8,Fvisitors to still see some animals in
OL,9,Fthe fields."
OL,11,FSark's former dairy closed in 2017 -
OL,12,Fmeaning milk, cream, butter and cheese
OL,13,Fwere imported from Guernsey until 2021.
OL,15,FThat year, the new facility was built
OL,16,Fat a cost of nearly #500,000 by the
OL,17,FSark Community Dairy Charitable Trust
OL,18,Fafter a large fundraising effort
OL,19,Fcollected islanders' donations.
