OL,3,CIsland loses its only dairy after
OL,4,Cnational appeal to find new farmers
OL,5,Cfails
OL,7,FKatherine and Jason were selected to
OL,8,Frun the farm following a worldwide
OL,9,Fsearch.
OL,11,FPaul Armorgie, a former Deputy and
OL,12,FConseiller of Sark's Chief Pleas,
OL,13,Fsaid: "I understand that the finances
OL,14,Fhave been a challenge and I must
OL,15,Fconfess, when I first saw the plans, I
OL,16,Fthought they're going to have to sell
OL,17,Fa lot of milk to cover that.
OL,19,F"I was slightly surprised by how
OL,20,Fambitious the plans were, but I wished
OL,21,Fthem every success."
