OL,3,CIsland loses its only dairy after
OL,4,Cnational appeal to find new farmers
OL,5,Cfails
OL,7,FKatherine says that with their family
OL,8,Fcalling them back to the UK, it was
OL,9,Ftime for the couple to head onto
OL,10,Fpastures new.
OL,12,FJason concludes, "We are really going
OL,13,Fto miss the community. It's not just
OL,14,Fthe dairy but the lifestyle that goes
OL,15,Fwith it that we'll miss as well - but
OL,16,Fwe will be back."
OL,18,FThough operations have now stopped, it
OL,19,Fis hoped that someone will yet step
OL,20,Fforward to revive Sark's milk industry.
